Author: unicorn6642
Text: Thank you, I'll look for an afternoon/evening job, thays when my bing cravings are the worst

Author: knivmord
Text: Idk if ur in school or not but if you’re not get a job!!! Then you’re away from the house for a few hours every day, if It’s a retail job you get some exercise (i used to walk 13000-15000 steps a day when i worked in a supermarket just at work) and you can control what you eat at ur break! The food can be triggering for some ppl but i found it the opposite, i kind of lived through what other people bought and any cravings i might have had was always gone after a shift.
